{"tid":999579,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/ PS4/ XBOX] Division 2","createTime":"2019-01-28T21:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T13:15:02.000Z","uid":73143,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b52e9afad600baf575f526204e398b6ca354cc","tid":999579,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T21:20:14.000Z","msg":"有無人會玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTom Clancy&rsquo;s The Division 2《湯姆克蘭西：全境封鎖 2》<br />\n<br />\n若華盛頓特區淪陷，人類文明也將崩壞瓦解<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓特區正在瀕臨瓦解邊緣。失控與不穩定正在威脅我們的社會，國會大廈發生政變的傳言使混亂加劇。所有國土戰略局的特工都迫切地想要在趁一切為時已晚之前拯救這座城市。<br />\n<br />\n你是國土戰略局的一員，是一群由平民特工組成的菁英團隊，你就是最後一道防線。華盛頓特區如今陷入危機，是時候全副武裝並使用獨特的技能解決這項新的威脅了。<br />\n<br />\n不同於先前任何一款遊戲，《全境封鎖 2》遊戲內的華盛頓 1 比 1 模擬真實城市，讓遊戲比以往更具真實性。遊戲地圖提供了對於地標、自然環境、鄰近地區與敵人藏身處極為詳盡的個人化視野。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fyWsKeyEiJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfyWsKeyEiJE&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OAB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=69a0a715\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fyWsKeyEiJE</a>"},{"pid":"801faa3af742fc08f49829ff8e47233565a095e6","tid":999579,"uid":74326,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T21:50:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ead565f5ce4ff913ab4682d9532b3743ab5d56a","tid":999579,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"801faa3af742fc08f49829ff8e47233565a095e6","tid":999579,"uid":74326,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T21:50:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 刷刷刷game評價好兩極"},{"pid":"138b1adb22889107917c655f4fc1facb0dc6141c","tid":999579,"uid":74326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:23:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92a4c6a901ef4a3416ce1391df4d3967054c53cd","tid":999579,"uid":171990,"like":0,